news.title: NGT directs authorities to connect 93 villages of Greater Noida with sewage network
news.para: The green panel noted the villages have been provided with internal drains but these are yet to be connected to the main sewer line.

news.title: Supertech to give structural audit info of twin towers as sought by CBRI by Aug 7
news.para: CBRI's approval is required for Edifice to go ahead with the charging -- rigging of the twin towers with explosives -- at the site, a process which would need them around 15 days.

news.title: Lucknow development body to release Rs 18 crore to spruce up its 15 RWAs
news.para: The Resident Welfare Associations (RWA) of the respective buildings will use the fund for maintenance and repairing of buildings, including the lifts and generators.
